        "timestamp": "2021-10-11 09:24:18.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> name of profile is 'skip-tests' not 'fast-build', please fix title\n\nI'm making the fast-build profile to not run the UI tests by using the \"maven.test.skip\" property to skip the tests in the UI POMs. This property is already configured in the profile and is the default property in maven for the purpose.\nI've added this property to the skip-tests too, as the intention of the profile is to skip tests.",
        "patchset_number": 1
